OL,3,CBlaze murder accused: 'I didn't want
OL,4,Cto hurt anyone but myself'
OL,6,FA man accused of murdering his former
OL,7,Fpartner's sister and her three young
OL,8,Fchildren by setting their house on
OL,9,Ffire has told a court: "I didn't want
OL,10,Fto hurt anyone but myself."
OL,12,FSharaz Ali had already told Doncaster
OL,13,FCrown Court he wanted to kill himself
OL,14,Fby setting himself alight and had no
OL,15,Fintention of harming others when the
OL,16,Fhouse in Bradford went up in flames on
OL,17,F21 August last year.
