OL,3,CBlaze murder accused: 'I didn't want
OL,4,Cto hurt anyone but myself'
OL,6,FThe incident on Westbury Road killed
OL,7,FBryonie Gawith, 29, and her children
OL,8,FDenisty Birtle, nine, Oscar Birtle,
OL,9,Ffive, and 22-month-old Aubree Birtle.
OL,11,FGiving evidence for a second day, Ali
OL,12,Fwas repeatedly asked by prosecutor
OL,13,FDavid Brooke KC why he failed to
OL,14,Frealise setting himself alight inside
OL,15,Fa house would threaten the lives of
OL,16,Fthose living there.
OL,18,FDuring cross-examination on Friday,
OL,19,FAli, 40, said: "It was the biggest
OL,20,Fmistake of my life and I regret it to
OL,21,Fthis day."
