OL,3,CBlaze murder accused: 'I didn't want
OL,4,Cto hurt anyone but myself'
OL,6,FHe told the jury: "I thought the fire
OL,7,Fwould stop at me. I wasn't thinking
OL,8,Fstraight."
OL,10,FThe defendant also said: "It was all
OL,11,Fan accident. I would never go there to
OL,12,Fhurt Bryonie and the kids."
OL,14,FHe said: "I didn't want to hurt anyone
OL,15,Fbut myself."
OL,17,FAli agreed with Mr Brooke that it was
OL,18,F"obvious" now that setting fire to
OL,19,Fyourself inside a house would mean the
OL,20,Fchildren upstairs would be seriously
OL,21,Fhurt or die.
