OL,3,CBlaze murder accused: 'I didn't want
OL,4,Cto hurt anyone but myself'
OL,6,FAli said: "But, at the time, I wasn't
OL,7,Fin my right frame of mind."
OL,9,FHe was also asked by prosecutor David
OL,10,FBrooke KC why he had decided to kill
OL,11,Fhimself in a way that would have been
OL,12,F"excruciatingly painful".
OL,14,FAli said: "I wasn't thinking straight."
OL,16,FThe prosecutor asked him when he first
OL,17,Fdecided on the plan to set himself
OL,18,Falight.
OL,20,FAli said: "I had no plan. I wasn't
OL,21,Fthinking straight."
