OL,3,CBlaze murder accused: 'I didn't want
OL,4,Cto hurt anyone but myself'
OL,6,FMiss Gawith's sister, Antonia,
OL,7,Fsurvived the fire, as did Ali, who
OL,8,Fsuffered severe injuries and was in an
OL,9,Finduced coma for months.
OL,11,FHe gave evidence in court on Friday
OL,12,Ffrom his wheelchair and with an oxygen
OL,13,Ftube in his nose.
OL,15,FAli admitted that he was upset on the
OL,16,Fnight of the fire because Antonia
OL,17,FGawith had broken up with him.
OL,19,FHe said he was drunk on vodka and had
OL,20,Falso taken cocaine.
