OL,3,CBlaze murder accused: 'I didn't want
OL,4,Cto hurt anyone but myself'
OL,6,FProsecutors say Ali was "motivated by
OL,7,Fjealousy and fuelled by drink and
OL,8,Fdrugs" when he set fire to the house,
OL,9,Fand went there to "take revenge" on
OL,10,FAntonia Gawith.
OL,12,FThe jury has seen doorbell footage of
OL,13,Fhim approach the property with his co-
OL,14,Faccused, Calum Sunderland, who was
OL,15,Fcarrying a petrol can and who kicked
OL,16,Fin the front door.
OL,18,FSunderland then runs away.
