OL,6,FAli, of no fixed address, and
OL,7,FSunderland, 26, of Calton Street,
OL,8,FKeighley, are charged with murdering
OL,9,FBryonie Gawith and the three children,
OL,10,Fand attempting to murder Antonia
OL,11,FGawith.
OL,13,FMohammed Shabir, 45, who had been due
OL,14,Fto go on trial with them, died of a
OL,15,Fheart attack last month after
OL,16,Fcollapsing in prison.
OL,18,FProsecutors say Shabir drove Ali and
OL,19,FSunderland to the house.
OL,21,FAli and Sunderland deny the charges.
